=====================
Author Identification
=====================

This is the code for author identification

Installation
============

Clone the repository

::

  git clone https://github.com/ivanvladimir/authorid.git


Intall python libraries

::

  sudo apt-get install build-essential python-dev python-setuptools
  sudo apt-get install libatlas-base-dev gfortran
  sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-scipy
  sudo apt-get install python-matplotlib


Install stanford libraries Core NLP

:: 

  mkdir lib
  wget http://nlp.stanford.edu/software/stanford-corenlp-full-2014-08-27.zip
  unzip stanford-corenlp-full-2014-08-27.zip
  cp stanford-corenlp-full-2014-08-27/stanford-corenlp-3.4.1.jar lib/
  cp stanford-corenlp-full-2014-08-27/stanford-corenlp-3.4.1-models.jar lib/


